data.title: The return of PAULA COLE
data.text:
VANITYSprisonB

YTCH

The return of PAULA COLE

Paula Cole was one of my absolute favorite artists to emerge from the 90's. Such a great songwriter and live performer!!! Most will remember her best for 'I Dont Want To Wait' (theme to 'Dawson's Creek') or 'Where Have All The Cowboys Gone?'..but there was so much more to her...

Her new album 'Courage' is out on 6/12 and you can listen to snippets here...

http://www.amazon.com/o/A...d_i=507846

Enjoy!

With new albums by Tori, Paula, Bjork, Joan Osborne..it does feel like the 90's again!!!!!

peace

[Edited 4/23/07 12:05pm]

Every minute of last night is on my face today....

VANITYSprisonB
